# Diagrams

Place architecture diagrams here (PNG, SVG, PlantUML, or draw.io files).

## Suggested diagrams
- `context-diagram.png` — C4 Level 1: System context
- `container-diagram.png` — C4 Level 2: Containers
- `component-diagram.png` — C4 Level 3: Components
- `domain-model.png` — DDD domain model
- `sequence-entry.png` — Vehicle entry sequence
- `sequence-exit.png` — Vehicle exit & payment sequence

